headline: AVEDA Launches in the U.S. Amazon Premium Beauty Store
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, May 28, 2025--AVEDA, a purpose-driven pioneer of plant-powered, high-performance beauty announces its debut in the U.S. Amazon Premium Beauty store, bringing its assortment of vegan hair, skin, body and lifestyle products to new consumers across the country.
